result.post_image_description: Four panels featuring Vivian and Belle from Zenless Zone Zero. Top left, Vivian with dark blue hair and an "N" hair clip, smiling with a yellow background and clovers. Top right, Belle with long white hair and a black bow, holding blue ice cream bars, smiling with a yellow background and clovers. Bottom left, Vivian with a serious expression, dark blue hair, and glowing blue eyes, against a pink background with hearts. Bottom right, Belle with a flustered expression, holding blue ice cream bars, against a pink background with question marks. Text overlays read "Ray of Sunshine," "Lord Pheonix," "Sunshine," and "Serious Mode." A watermark reads "CesarZebrah."
